"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
"   <div>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials contributorType\" href=\"UTD.htm?2/9/2202/contributors\">",
"     Section Editors",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?2/9/2202/contributors\">",
"     John K Triedman, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?2/9/2202/contributors\">",
"     Samuel L&eacute;vy, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?2/9/2202/contributors\">",
"     Samuel Asirvatham, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
"   <div>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials contributorType\" href=\"UTD.htm?2/9/2202/contributors\">",
"     Deputy Editor",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?2/9/2202/contributors\">",
"     Brian C Downey, MD, FACC",
